{"tid":2190973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"油麻地一名男子被拘捕，涉嫌管有第1部毒藥被捕","createTime":"2020-09-06T06:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T06:12:43.000Z","uid":222970,"like":12,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"054a229f4bcd8e32abacd393f1668074ff68f63d","tid":2190973,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:22:29.000Z","msg":"【油麻地一名男子涉藏違禁藥物被捕】<br />\n<br />\n中午12時許，警方在油麻地進行反罪惡巡邏期間，在南京街及白加士街附近截查一名男子，並搜出手套、口罩及一排藥丸，涉嫌管有第1部毒藥被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方會繼續在現場及附近一帶加強巡邏，嚴正執法，以保障社區安全。由於有網民發起今日在九龍區一帶進行未經批准集結，警方呼籲市民前往該區時留意安全，如遇任何可疑事件或發現可疑物品，請即向警方舉報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bByu23M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbByu23M.jpg&h=1a68e746&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4WAeas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4WAeas.jpg&h=793d3928&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac34d12daad90f9cbf2d694d7f0e84d356537bc4","tid":2190973,"uid":222970,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"裝修廢料啱啱仲未柒完？依家又想沖出嚟柒？<br />\n<br />\n油麻地後巷發現多袋磚頭及碎石 警方檢走追查物主身分<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2190893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2190893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90d37e3b47811c8c8704a4d66f92caa67d8d0682","tid":2190973,"uid":357885,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"又搵到偉哥?"},{"pid":"ef36baa48e62705bd703563508a09ee175290fd2","tid":2190973,"uid":4239,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"似地盤工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f05d23f365f572a48d36ffaafb61224d4be7fb","tid":2190973,"uid":109345,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"咩藥<br />\n手套都唔比帶？"},{"pid":"900624d4abd3073f2ee480c28d52d6bc554e9561","tid":2190973,"uid":138964,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"rep